data.description: Welcome to your dream townhome in the prestigious Glendale Lakes subdivision! This gorgeous two-bedroom, two-and-a-half bathroom gem is a true find. Nestled in a peaceful setting backing to the lush fairways of the golf course, you'll enjoy tranquility and stunning views from your own backyard. As you step inside, you will be greeted by a beautiful designed layout, as the kicthen opens to your cozy living room which overlooks the beautiful golf course. Upstairs, you'll find two generously sized bedrooms, the master bedroom has its own private full bath, and a wall of closet space. Other highlights of this townhome include a convenient main level powder room, a laundry area, and a one-car attached garage for your convenience. The Glendale Lakes subdivision offers a fantastic community, with easy access to golfing, and overall outdoor enjoyment. This townhome is not just a place to live; it's a lifestyle. With excellent schools, shopping, dining, and major routes nearby such as North Ave and 355. This gem wont last long!
